    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>You could try <a href=\"http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=42094\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">JarSpy</a>.  There is an IDEA plugin version of it that I use.</p>\n"
