      "body" : "FYI, You may need to add <code>C:\\Program Files\\Java\\jdk&lt;version&gt;\\bin</code> to your system or user PATH environment variable before you can use <code>jar</code> as a system command. (Where &lt;version&gt; is your jdk version-build number. Check it in <code>C:\\Program Files\\Java</code>)"
